Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:02.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:09.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:11.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你那是什么表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:15.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那不是咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:17.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈不是喝不了咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:19.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么要买那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:24.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也差不多要成为大人了 以为自己能喝就买了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:26.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:33.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你哪里像大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:36.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就算是我也有很多地方有成长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:39.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那早苗就能喝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:42.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我能喝啊 而且还是黑咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:48.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,黑咖啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:53.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个换给你喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:57.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 我是大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.37,0:00:58.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:00:59.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:00.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:01.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快换给我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:03.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:10.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:12.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:15.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘛 也有喝不了咖啡的大人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:17.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过你还是个小孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:19.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:31.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大人可不会干这种事
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:17.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天又被高木同学捉弄了一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过 明天一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:33.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:37.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天一个人走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:38.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么 一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:41.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是高木同学不是骑车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:51.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我推着就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:55.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,空罐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:03.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那罐果汁 是最近新推出的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:04.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:06.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这难道是什么陷阱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:09.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要不要尝一口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:12.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:13.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:21.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 虽然我不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:25.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样其实是间接接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:28.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哼哼哼 怎么样啊 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思了吧 你就难为情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她一点也不难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个人究竟怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,给你 谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:43.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喝啊 我完全不介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么 这点小事不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是间接接吻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我看看 垃圾桶在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:20.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你还真能投进去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:29.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一顺手就投出去了 没想到竟然能投中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:43.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我原来还有这种才能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:47.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 我也来试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:06:01.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你往哪里扔啊 根本够不着嘛高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你要和我比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,无所谓 反正我是不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:13.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么我们轮流投 先投进者为胜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然发起没有胜算的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看来高木同学已经气昏头了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这感觉真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:28.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是高木同学赢了 你要我做什么我都听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:30.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,待会儿不准反悔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:33.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:36.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过我不会输就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:39.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我要扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:52.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是你没投中 就是我的胜利了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又被她摆了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,站在刚才的位置上 用同样的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:07.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我能行 我一定能投进去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:13.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是西片赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就把我的初吻给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你还问是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就在我投的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:41.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:43.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好的 要遵守约定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要让你干什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 她想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:07:59.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就算不让你做什么也没什么不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:04.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:09.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 高木同学 那不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你这样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我感觉我一辈子都没办法赢过你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:14.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正你也赢不了我 这不挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:20.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思啊 我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:22.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,碳酸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太辣舌头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}此处日语的「辛い」，专指食物对口腔舌头的刺激、刺痛感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你那是什么表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那不是碳酸汽水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈不是喝不了碳酸汽水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:40.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,碳酸为什么会这么辣舌头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:43.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么总买些自己喝不了的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又在装大人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是呢 我喜欢这个味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:53.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「嗡」地一下来劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:53.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}日语「ツンてきた」，意为某些味道对鼻腔的强烈刺激后的表情、反应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的舌头 我的舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你真吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:09:00.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉喝了碳酸汽水之后也会这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:01.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你喝喝看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,脑子绝对会「嗡」的一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不会啦 不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其实是来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「嗡」的一下究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:29.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的会有那种反应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 想打嗝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有反应了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:39.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在这种时候打嗝肯定会被她们嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我快要忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:50.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,已经忍不住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:56.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又「嗡」地来劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:01.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,给我走着瞧 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,加上回家路上被捉弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天被她捉弄了十五次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在比赛中出现失误的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:34.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,作为给自己的惩罚 我会进行十倍的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:38.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我相信这样做能让我在下一次夺取胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:40.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:44.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是被捉弄了十五次 乘上十倍就是一百五十次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,第一次做的话 没什么难度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,总之先做三倍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:58.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一 二 三 四…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,十八
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:04.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,十九
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:09.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,二十…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比想象中难多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:14.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,稍微减少一点次数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:15.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:20.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这是给平日被捉弄了太多次的自己的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:28.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一边体会痛苦 一边提高警惕防止下次重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,加油啊 我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:33.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肌肉锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的手臂怎么了 受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:44.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么 只是普通的肌肉酸痛罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:51.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,别这样 真的很疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,刚刚的要算一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:57.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这时我应该对自己严格一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就记一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:07.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被骗了吧 肌肉酸痛挺严重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这次是的的确确地被捉弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:15.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么突然肌肉酸痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个 我从昨天开始锻炼肌肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊 要是不三天打鱼两天晒网就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:25.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哼 你就尽管说吧 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:33.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么 今天被高木同学捉弄的次数是二十三次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这不是比昨天还多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:42.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一 二 三…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你还在坚持锻炼肌肉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 姑且有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:51.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 你真的坚持下来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,托你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:55.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:01.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,据说成长期时肌肉锻炼过度的话会长不高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:05.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:08.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来 我也好像在哪里听说过…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:09.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:12.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是让高木同学长得比我还高的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那她不就会更变本加厉地捉弄我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么办 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:20.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过那好像只是谣言而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:21.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原来是谣言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:26.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不如说 适度的肌肉锻炼可以促进身高发育呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:31.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是这样 所以你就安心继续锻炼肌肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我觉得这样很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然只有一点点 但感觉你比以前变得结实了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:40.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 一言不发的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道说你害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,害 害羞什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:54.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你脸红了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,果然 你害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 你干嘛总是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:04.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都说了 因为你的反应很有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:08.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过 你比以前结实了是实话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,变得有点帅气了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的脸比刚才更红了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:18.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是这样的 是因为天气太热了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:21.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我说 等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到头来 今天被她捉弄了五十四次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算上刚刚那次就是五十五次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:30.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过 我决定就算不被高木同学捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:32.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也要坚持锻炼肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:35.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,配音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:40.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,乔尼先生 今晚要不要来咱家吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 这要看工作忙不忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:45.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是很晚才能下班 我就和次郎吃了再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:50.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然和次郎打好关系也不错 偶尔也来一下咱家嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,人家最近很寂寞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:55.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我要工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:58.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,差不多该回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 再玩一会儿也没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:04.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么要讲关西腔啊 听到就烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:08.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太过分了 你一点也不在乎人家的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你这么说也太小气了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也是很拼命的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你哭什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:20.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为 乔尼先生和次郎都陷入工作无法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:23.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,人家已经不能忍耐下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,突然变成修罗场了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:28.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太过分了 太过分了乔尼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是你是这种态度的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:38.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:43.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那两只猫 都是公的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那 应该叫乔尼前辈才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:50.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,呀 这不是次郎吗 一起去吃饭如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,回家吧 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:57.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,伞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:09.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然在放学时开始下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 我可没听说今天会下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:14.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我没带雨衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:15.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,冒失鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:19.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗 你对美奈太严格啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:22.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我们搭巴士回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我没带钱搭巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,超级冒失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我借给你吧 巴士票而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:35.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶 今天也被捉弄得够呛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:39.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不回家吗 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:43.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个 我忘带伞和雨衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:49.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你还真是冒失啊 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不知道今天会下雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的太冒失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,竟然没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:03.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我记得西片的伞挺大的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:12.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的相合伞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么会发生这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 感觉这样好尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,说些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:25.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学 你的自行车怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我明天走路上学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:29.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:35.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉刚才的气氛尴尬的要命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉要窒息了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:41.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不赶紧做些什么缓和这种气氛的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:50.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被吓到了吧 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:00.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:05.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶 不愧是高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这种程度的恶作剧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么湿哒哒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你太大惊小怪了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:25.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,话说回来 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你那边的肩膀淋湿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只淋湿了一点儿 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:32.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行 会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:35.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再凑近一点 好好地躲到伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:48.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心脏跳动的声音 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:56.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是被高木同学发现我很紧张 她一定会来捉弄我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:59.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,总之 不说些什么的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:07.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学竟然忘记带伞 真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:11.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道说 高木同学出人意料地是个冒失鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:15.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道我说得太过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:22.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可能也有些健忘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学承认自己有些健忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这是什么展开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:33.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感觉自己好像赢了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:36.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,刚才我也忘了一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:38.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样吗 忘了事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:40.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是什么事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:45.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,像现在这样 形容两个人打着同一把伞走路的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:48.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:51.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我有点想不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:54.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:56.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,相合伞…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我听不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:11.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是相合伞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你肯定没有忘记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:17.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个是叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:24.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,情侣之间为了表达爱意 用自己的嘴唇去接触对方嘴唇那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:27.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可恶 答不上来就输了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,亲 亲吻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:33.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 雨声太大 我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雨势已经比刚才小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:39.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要装作没听见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是亲吻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:43.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 是的是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:48.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有 不是有情侣用来表达心情的词吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:50.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:53.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看 就是那个比「喜欢」更进一步的词
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:54.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:57.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,开头的第一个字是「a」的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:57.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}这里高木想说的词是日语的「我爱你」 即愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:20:59.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:02.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,下一个字是「i」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我猜不出来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么 换成英文的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是「I」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接下来是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:18.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「I」「lo」的下一个字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:24.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最后一个字是「you」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:26.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:30.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:40.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雨停了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:42.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:46.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了 我还以为要坚持到高木同学家门口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:47.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,害得我提心吊胆的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那么 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.04,0:21:52.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我走这边回去 再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:58.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我忘记回家的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:03.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 饶了我吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:37.53,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:41.91,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:52.25,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:02:01.10,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:09.35,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.32,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:17.70,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:21.62,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:25.50,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:33.59,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:41.89,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:47.31,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:51.31,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:03:01.53,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:37.53,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:41.91,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:52.25,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:02:01.10,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校园的庭院 第一个发现你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:09.35,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你说些什么呢 即便是想着这些也是一种乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.32,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗帘随风起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:17.70,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不经意地投入一束阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:21.62,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美丽的容颜笑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:25.50,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:33.59,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}风儿喧嚣 似要吹散考试的忧郁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:41.89,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}呐 我想要和你一起 立下两人的秘密约定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:47.31,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}会错意了也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:51.31,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 这样想着却不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:03:01.53,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}弥漫在周围的那阵幽香 想在你的身边静静感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:28.87,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}「目を覚ましてよ」 君の声が僕を包み Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:37.25,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窓を開けて　そよ風が君の髪をなびく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:41.67,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}部屋から出る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:48.34,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}僕の腕をつかみながら　君は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.43,0:22:57.44,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}「もう少しだけ」「もう少しだけ」と 僕に　君は呟く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.44,0:23:09.53,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}この世界が闇に染まる前に この思いを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:17.29,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}だからお願い　僕の傍にいてくれないか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:19.62,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}君が好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:25.05,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}この思いが君に届くように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:30.51,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}願いが叶いますように
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:28.87,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}「起床了哦」你的声音环绕着我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:37.25,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}推开窗户 你的秀发随微风飘扬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:41.67,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}走出房间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:48.34,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你挽着我的手臂 轻声呢喃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.43,0:22:57.44,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}「再陪我一会儿 再陪我一会儿」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.44,0:23:09.53,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}我要把这思念传达给你 在世界被染上黑暗之前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:17.29,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}所以拜托了 请留在我身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:19.62,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}因为我是如此地爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:25.05,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}愿这思念能传达到你的心里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:30.51,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}希望这一切都能化为现实
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——STAFF——
